            "text": "Comprehensive panel including inflammatory markers, RF, ANA, thyroid function (TSH within normal range confirming adequate levothyroxine dosing), and fibromyalgia workup; mildly elevated CRP and weakly positive ANA noted, prompting rheumatological referral for further evaluation of possible early autoimmune aetiology."
